of being important.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.920
-I don't see it as a
failure of the young,

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:05.480
I see it as a failure
of the elders.

00:08:05.480 --> 00:08:08.920
So we, as elders, we
have responsibility.

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:12.530
We have the choice
to speak, to teach,

00:08:12.530 --> 00:08:17.835
to show, and hope and bring
the young along with us.

00:08:55.600 --> 00:09:02.310
