00:12:50.950 --> 00:12:53.470
That's what rites
of passage told me.

00:12:53.470 --> 00:12:58.280
Assist that person's
growth so that when

00:12:58.280 --> 00:13:01.588
their gift is revealed to the
world, the world will benefit.

00:13:01.588 --> 00:13:02.963
That's an adult's
