00:15:27.090 --> 00:15:30.450
So what is your medicine?

00:15:30.450 --> 00:15:33.950
And how will I face my
life's coming challenges?

00:15:33.950 --> 00:15:35.920
How will I get to
be that man or woman

00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:39.620
