answers to these questions?

00:16:20.310 --> 00:16:23.350
Who is out there to
support them in uncovering

00:16:23.350 --> 00:16:25.840
answers to these
questions for themselves?

00:16:25.840 --> 00:16:27.960
And then, the biggest
question I've asked myself

00:16:27.960 --> 00:16:32.250
is, are rites of passage and
mentorship the missing link

00:16:32.250 --> 00:16:34.140
in youth development?

00:16:34.140 --> 00:16:36.660
In a sense, what I would
call the unifying field

00:16:36.660 --> 00:16:41.615
theory of youth development,
almost a silver bullet perhaps.

00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:49.540
So this is the bucket of
challenges that's facing us.

00:16:49.540 --> 00:16:52.030
You saw some of
