before, during,

00:17:04.109 --> 00:17:10.349
and after any kind of initiation
or rite of passage process.

00:17:10.349 --> 00:17:14.060
That's just one set of problems,
there's also another problem.

00:17:14.060 --> 00:17:18.250
If we don't initiate girls
and boys when they're young,

00:17:18.250 --> 00:17:20.344
they grow up and they
live out their lives

00:17:20.344 --> 00:17:23.050
in suspended adolescence.

00:17:23.050 --> 00:17:27.619
And yeah, Charlie Sheen is the
perfect poster boy for that,

00:17:27.619 --> 00:17:30.330
but in fact, take a look around.

00:17:30.330 --> 00:17:33.790
We have adults, quote
unquote, "living out

00:17:33.790 --> 00:17:36.760
their suspended adolescence"
in all kinds of institutions

00:17:36.760 --> 00:17:39.670
across this country.

00:17:39.670 --> 00:17:43.500
Government I tend to think of
as Animal House half the time.

00:17:43.500 --> 00:17:44.090
You know?

00:17:44.090 --> 00:17:45.675
It's a fraternity gone crazy.

00:17:48.700 --> 00:17:51.233
Corporations,
other institutions.

00:17:54.040 --> 00:17:56.372
So we're all paying
a price for that,

00:17:56.372 --> 00:18:03.790
for the uninitiated serving
in these capacities.

