00:18:54.080 --> 00:18:58.870
To me, that's emblematic
of stepping into maturity

00:18:58.870 --> 00:19:03.890
consciously and I really am
curious to see what other steps

00:19:03.890 --> 00:19:07.110
Google might be taking
