00:48:32.550 --> 00:48:35.340
and exactly what doses and how
to make this process something

00:48:35.340 --> 00:48:37.840
you could almost
count on for people

00:48:37.840 --> 00:48:40.890
who are dealing with cancer
or dying and stuff like that.

00:48:40.890 --> 00:48:44.140
But is there a way to
use research and science

00:48:44.140 --> 00:48:48.097
to understand what these
