00:48:55.570 --> 00:48:59.200
But I think everyone would agree
depression's bad, suicide's

00:48:59.200 --> 00:49:02.450
bad, binge drinking's
bad, and all that stuff.

00:49:02.450 --> 00:49:05.240
But to have the cultural
shift to understand

00:49:05.240 --> 00:49:07.550
that it's something that
