00:50:18.800 --> 00:50:22.550
for high school boys who attend
their program, et cetera.

00:50:22.550 --> 00:50:25.760
But by and large, we're still
in the very early stages

00:50:25.760 --> 00:50:29.090
of the scientific evidence
that you're alluding to.

00:50:29.090 --> 00:50:31.010
But the whole issue of
drugs that you raise

00:50:31.010 --> 00:50:33.510
is also an interesting
one, because certainly

00:50:33.510 --> 00:50:35.640
many indigenous cultures
throughout the planet

00:50:35.640 --> 00:50:42.260
use psychotropic plants as part
of the initiation ceremonies.

00:50:42.260 --> 00:50:44.640
In fact, Iowaska--
which most of you

00:50:44.640 --> 00:50:46.490
are probably familiar
with, it's come now

00:50:46.490 --> 00:50:49.620
to North America
from South America--

00:50:49.620 --> 00:50:53.160
was used fundamentally for
that purpose for many years.

00:50:53.160 --> 00:50:55.700
And there's also
Martin Prechtel,

00:50:55.700 --> 00:50:59.570
who wrote many wonderful
books about Central American

00:50:59.570 --> 00:51:02.390
initiation, the
native Mayan people.

00:51:02.390 --> 00:51:06.140
One of the things that he talked
about was how one of the first

00:51:06.140 --> 00:51:09.010
exercises they would
do with the elders--

00:51:09.010 --> 00:51:10.990
they'd take the boys
out in the wilderness

00:51:10.990 --> 00:51:13.720
and get them drunk as
skunks so that they

00:51:13.720 --> 00:51:16.700
could begin to experience that,
but in a safe and contained

00:51:16.700 --> 00:51:17.780
way.

00:51:17.780 --> 00:51:21.450
So that's the best answer I can
give you, I'm afraid, for now.

00:51:21.450 --> 00:51:22.560
