that nothing else matters,

00:52:18.490 --> 00:52:21.890
because you are feeling
things in a way-- in the fiber

00:52:21.890 --> 00:52:23.970
of your bodyy-- that can't
be ignored regardless

00:52:23.970 --> 00:52:27.095
of what you thought
before or anything else.

00:52:27.095 --> 00:52:27.970
FREDERICK MARX: Yeah.

00:52:27.970 --> 00:52:32.300
Well again, the
scientific evidence

00:52:32.300 --> 00:52:34.180
