00:52:57.620 --> 00:53:01.880
Parents; high schools;
colleges and universities;

00:53:01.880 --> 00:53:04.530
therapists, counselors,
psychologists;

00:53:04.530 --> 00:53:08.300
youth development centers;
and faith-based institutions.

00:53:08.300 --> 00:53:11.410
So we're basically
offering them ideas

00:53:11.410 --> 00:53:14.280
for curricula, how
they can implement

00:53:14.280 --> 00:53:16.970
some of these practices
into their own cultures.

00:53:16.970 --> 00:53:19.720
So places like
YMCAs, for example.

00:53:19.720 --> 00:53:22.820
So please, go online and help
yourselves to these things.

00:53:22.820 --> 00:53:24.910
We're giving them away.

00:53:24.910 --> 00:53:26.950
And there's a lot of
helpful tools in there,

00:53:26.950 --> 00:53:28.990
especially if any
of you are parents.

00:53:28.990 --> 00:53:31.050
Most of you are probably
too young to have teens,

00:53:31.050 --> 00:53:33.510
but at any rate, if
